      <story-so-far>
        <reasoning>Passage shows the defenders' planned layered defense put to the test, a series of coordinated assaults, a failed solo attempt to sever the enemy command node, and then a collective gambit that forced the command node to surface and be destroyed. I added bullets for the sequence of attacks (east neutralized by Remedy, north stalled, northwest false weakness overcommitted), Runner's failed solo underground attempt, the group's decision to force the command node upward (Velvet+Runner downward growth, Remedy chemicals, Holloway protecting Kira), and the destruction of the command node leading to the attackers losing coordination and withdrawing. I consolidated or removed now-irrelevant operational minutiae (e.g., Velvet's exact % completion, earlier estimates of time to readiness) and merged prior leadership/context bullets (Florence's confession and her shift to collaboration) into fewer, plot-relevant lines. I updated character/resource statuses to reflect depletion and injuries described in this passage (Runner torn/leaking, Velvet withered/depleted, Remedy chemically exhausted, facility badly damaged but defenses holding and core systems intact). I kept the chronology clear and focused on events that will matter going forward: the command node's destruction, the group's demonstrated ability to improvise and trust, and the defenders' battered condition.</reasoning>
        <summary>
          - FTL shuttle crash killed Jensen and Reed; Kira survived with head and rib injuries; ship AI SAM remains offline and emergency neural-link AI Buddy active.
          - Holloway plant collective rescued and treated Kira; Scout bonded as a loyal perimeter scout and stays close to Kira in the central core.
          - Florence publicly confessed fabricating Elder Twist's pronouncements and was initially isolated and distrusted; she remains tactical coordinator but has shifted toward genuine collaboration with the group.
          - Hostile plants labeled Kira “contamination” and launched a coordinated multi-pronged assault that breached outer sections; defenders contracted to a defensible core and stabilized.
          - Defenders implemented a layered defense (Runner underground misdirection/monitoring, Velvet multilayer barriers, Remedy chemical traps); early exchanges caused injuries and resource depletion but bought time.
          - New coordinated attack began: bioluminescent signaling united hostile forces; eastern assault punched through the first barrier and was neutralized by Remedy's chemical trap.
          - Northern approach was stalled by Velvet's barriers and Runner severing roots; hostiles probed multiple directions to find weaknesses.
          - Hostiles exploited the prepared northwest false weakness and committed overwhelming forces; the trap began to fail and simultaneous southern pressure started, surrounding the defenders.
          - Runner attempted a solo underground approach to sever a suspected command node but was intercepted and could not reach it; Runner surfaced badly torn and leaking.
          - Group decision to act collectively: Velvet and Runner combined downward growth toward the command node location while Remedy supplied growth accelerants and withering compounds and Holloway prepared to protect Kira and the core.
          - The combined effort forced a massive hostile command node to surface inside the facility's defensive perimeter; defenders attacked in unison (Velvet constriction, Runner severing, Remedy dissolution, Holloway blocking).
          - The hostile command node was destroyed; bioluminescent coordination signals cut off and attacking plants lost cohesion and withdrew.
          - Aftermath: attackers retreated; the facility is heavily damaged but defenses are holding and core life-support/medical systems remain intact; defenders are exhausted and depleted (Runner severely injured/leaking, Velvet withered/depleted, Remedy's chemical reserves exhausted, Holloway drained).
          - Group dynamics: the team improvised a solution together, demonstrating practical trust and collaboration; Florence is less isolated and acknowledges the group's collective effectiveness, marking fragile but significant progress.
        </summary>
